summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the improvement of 45th Avenue South from South Holly Street to South Willow Street; and certain other streets, avenues and alleys, by paving and other improving the same; as authorized by Ordinance No. 93985, creating Local Improvement District No. 6320; eliminating a certain street and avenue from said local improvement district and amending Section 1 of said ordinance; paving, etc.
